@startuml Tích hợp Google Drive API
title Sơ đồ tích hợp Google Drive API - Upload file media

actor "Giáo viên" as Teacher
participant "React\nFrontend" as Frontend
participant "FileUploadController" as Controller
participant "FileUploadService" as Service
participant "GoogleDriveService" as DriveService
participant "Google Drive API" as DriveAPI
database "MySQL" as DB

== Upload file audio cho Listening ==

Teacher -> Frontend: Chọn file audio (MP3)
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Frontend: Validate file\n(type, size < 50MB)

Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/files/upload\nMultipartFile + metadata
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: uploadFile(file, type, testId)
activate Service

Service -> Service: Generate unique filename\nfilename = "listening_part1_" + UUID

Service -> DriveService: uploadToDrive(file, filename, folderId)
activate DriveService

DriveService -> DriveAPI: OAuth2 Authentication
activate DriveAPI
DriveAPI --> DriveService: Access Token
deactivate DriveAPI

DriveService -> DriveAPI: Create file metadata\n{name, parents, mimeType}
activate DriveAPI
DriveAPI --> DriveService: File ID
deactivate DriveAPI

DriveService -> DriveAPI: Upload file content
activate DriveAPI
DriveAPI --> DriveService: Upload success
deactivate DriveAPI

DriveService -> DriveAPI: Set permission\n{type: "anyone", role: "reader"}
activate DriveAPI
DriveAPI --> DriveService: Permission set
deactivate DriveAPI

DriveService -> DriveAPI: Get file URL
activate DriveAPI
DriveAPI --> DriveService: webContentLink
deactivate DriveAPI

DriveService --> Service: File URL
deactivate DriveService

Service -> DB: INSERT INTO media_file\n(filename, url, type, size)
activate DB
DB --> Service: media_file_id
deactivate DB

Service -> DB: UPDATE question_group\nSET audio_url = ?
activate DB
DB --> Service: Success
deactivate DB

Service --> Controller: {fileId, url, filename}
deactivate Service

Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK\n{url, message}
deactivate Controller

Frontend --> Teacher: Hiển thị thông báo thành công\nPreview audio player
deactivate Frontend

@enduml

@startuml Tích hợp Gmail SMTP
title Sơ đồ tích hợp Gmail SMTP - Gửi email thông báo

participant "ExamAttemptService" as ExamService
participant "EmailService" as EmailService
participant "Thymeleaf\nTemplate Engine" as Template
participant "JavaMailSender" as MailSender
participant "Gmail SMTP\nServer" as SMTP
actor "Học viên" as Student

== Gửi email kết quả thi ==

ExamService -> ExamService: submitAttempt()\nChấm điểm xong

ExamService -> EmailService: sendExamResultEmail(user, attempt)
activate EmailService

EmailService -> EmailService: Prepare email data\n{userName, testTitle, bandScore, correctCount}

EmailService -> Template: process("exam-result.html", data)
activate Template
Template -> Template: Render HTML template\nwith user data
Template --> EmailService: HTML content
deactivate Template

EmailService -> MailSender: createMimeMessage()
activate MailSender
MailSender --> EmailService: MimeMessage
deactivate MailSender

EmailService -> EmailService: Set email properties:\n- To: user.email\n- Subject: "Kết quả thi IELTS"\n- Content: HTML\n- Encoding: UTF-8

EmailService -> MailSender: send(message)
activate MailSender

MailSender -> SMTP: Connect to smtp.gmail.com:587
activate SMTP
SMTP --> MailSender: Connection established
deactivate SMTP

MailSender -> SMTP: STARTTLS (Enable encryption)
activate SMTP
SMTP --> MailSender: TLS enabled
deactivate SMTP

MailSender -> SMTP: AUTH LOGIN\n(username, app password)
activate SMTP
SMTP --> MailSender: Authentication success
deactivate SMTP

MailSender -> SMTP: MAIL FROM: davictory.ielts@gmail.com
activate SMTP
SMTP --> MailSender: OK
deactivate SMTP

MailSender -> SMTP: RCPT TO: user@email.com
activate SMTP
SMTP --> MailSender: OK
deactivate SMTP

MailSender -> SMTP: DATA (email content)
activate SMTP
SMTP --> MailSender: OK
deactivate SMTP

MailSender -> SMTP: QUIT
activate SMTP
SMTP --> MailSender: Goodbye
deactivate SMTP

MailSender --> EmailService: Email sent successfully
deactivate MailSender

EmailService -> EmailService: Log success:\n"Email sent to user@email.com"

EmailService --> ExamService: Success
deactivate EmailService

note over SMTP, Student
  Gmail SMTP server xử lý
  và gửi email đến hộp thư
  của học viên
end note

SMTP -> Student: Email delivered

Student -> Student: Mở email\nXem kết quả thi

@enduml

