@startuml Xử lý lỗi khi gửi email
title Cơ chế xử lý lỗi và retry khi gửi email

participant "Service" as Service
participant "EmailService" as Email
participant "Gmail SMTP" as SMTP
database "Email Queue\n(MySQL)" as Queue

Service -> Email: sendEmailAsync(to, subject, content)
activate Email

Email -> Email: CompletableFuture.runAsync()

Email -> SMTP: Send email
activate SMTP

alt Email gửi thành công
    SMTP --> Email: Success
    deactivate SMTP
    Email -> Email: Log success
    
else Lỗi kết nối
    SMTP --> Email: MailSendException
    deactivate SMTP
    Email -> Email: Log error
    Email -> Queue: INSERT INTO email_queue\n(to, subject, content, retry_count=0)
    activate Queue
    Queue --> Email: Queued
    deactivate Queue
    
else Lỗi authentication
    SMTP --> Email: AuthenticationFailedException
    deactivate SMTP
    Email -> Email: Log critical error
    Email -> Email: Alert admin
    
else Lỗi recipient không tồn tại
    SMTP --> Email: MailSendException (550)
    deactivate SMTP
    Email -> Email: Log invalid recipient
    Email -> Email: Mark email as failed
end

deactivate Email

== Retry mechanism (Scheduled job) ==

loop Mỗi 5 phút
    Email -> Queue: SELECT * FROM email_queue\nWHERE retry_count < 3\nAND next_retry_at <= NOW()
    activate Queue
    Queue --> Email: List<EmailQueue>
    deactivate Queue
    
    loop Cho mỗi email trong queue
        Email -> SMTP: Retry send email
        activate SMTP
        
        alt Thành công
            SMTP --> Email: Success
            deactivate SMTP
            Email -> Queue: DELETE FROM email_queue\nWHERE id = ?
            activate Queue
            Queue --> Email: Deleted
            deactivate Queue
            
        else Vẫn lỗi
            SMTP --> Email: Failed
            deactivate SMTP
            Email -> Queue: UPDATE email_queue\nSET retry_count = retry_count + 1,\nnext_retry_at = NOW() + INTERVAL 10 MINUTE
            activate Queue
            Queue --> Email: Updated
            deactivate Queue
        end
    end
end

note over Email, Queue
  **Retry strategy:**
  - Retry tối đa 3 lần
  - Delay giữa các lần retry: 10 phút
  - Sau 3 lần retry thất bại, đánh dấu failed
  - Admin được thông báo về email failed
end note

@enduml
